        "Description": [
          {
            "text": "Say goodbye to lukewarm lunches, wilted groceries, and soggy food deliveries! Our Large Insulated Cooler Bag with Zippered closure is designed to revolutionize food transport for delivery services, catering, and everyday use. Crafted from high-quality polyester, this durable, portable tote features a refined dual-slider zipper for secure closure and reinforced 'no tear' handles to withstand heavy loads. The spacious interior (22x14x13 inches) easily accommodates multiple meal containers, grocery bags with chilled dairy and meats, or catering supplies, keeping frozen items frozen and hot items hot for hours. Its collapsible design saves storage space, while the leak-proof construction ensures mess-free transport. Ideal for Doordash, Grubhub, catering businesses, camping, travel, beach trips, and sustainable grocery shopping. Customizable with printed logos, this wholesale promotional bag is perfect for branded giveaways, bulk orders, or personal use. Make every delivery a success and every outing convenient with this reliable, insulated cooler bag.",
